ZH: 我们将在下个星期召开会议。
EN: We will hold a meeting next week.

ZH: 公司经理周三将召开全体员工会议。
EN: The company manager will convene a staff meeting on Wednesday.

ZH: 请问什么时候召开这次会议？
EN: May I ask when the meeting will be held?

ZH: 政府决定召开紧急记者发布会。
EN: The government decided to convene an emergency press conference.

ZH: 学校将在周五召开家长会。
EN: The school will hold a parent teacher meeting on Friday.

ZH: 大使馆今天将召开新闻发布会。
EN: The embassy will convene a press conference today.

ZH: 公司决定召开一个新的培训班。
EN: The company decided to hold a new training session.

ZH: 会议召开的时间比预计的要晚。
EN: The meeting was convened later than expected.

ZH: 公司将在本周召开一次全员大会。
EN: The company will hold a general meeting this week.

ZH: 总统将在明天召开紧急电视讲话。
EN: The president will convene an emergency televised address tomorrow.

ZH: 如果有问题，请召开一个临时会议。
EN: Call an ad-hoc meeting if there are any issues.

ZH: 领导者们决定召开一个策略性会议。
EN: The leaders decided to convene a strategic meeting.

ZH: 我们需要召开一次特别会议来讨论这个问题。
EN: We need to hold a special meeting to discuss this issue.

ZH: 我们的会议室已经被预定好了，准备召开会议。
EN: Our meeting room has been booked, ready for the meeting to be held.

ZH: 公司计划下周召开员工培训课程。
EN: The company plans to hold an employee training session next week.

ZH: 我们需要召开一个研讨会来解决这个难题。
EN: We need to convene a workshop to solve this problem.

ZH: 准备好召开这个项目的总结会。
EN: Prepare to convene a wrap-up meeting for this project.

ZH: 上周召开的会议决定了下一步的计划。
EN: The meeting held last week determined the next steps in the plan.

ZH: 在公司每个月召开例会是必要的。
EN: Holding regular meetings in the company every month is necessary.

ZH: 我们决定在明天召开一次小组会议。
EN: We decided to hold a group meeting tomorrow.
